nan hendthi &lt;unk&gt; ( kannada : &lt;unk&gt; ನ ಹೆಂಡ ತಿ ) is a 1987 indian kannada film , directed by dinesh babu and produced by rockline venkatesh . the film stars ananth nag , ramakrishna , sharan and doddanna among others . the film is based on the novel of the same name by saisuthe . the film stars ananth nag , ramakrishna , sharan and doddanna among others .